name: Kyoto Animation | Style LoRA | 京アニ スタイル
description:
KYOTO ANIMATIONS

Style LoRA

(EN/日本語/中文)

|___________________________________________________________________________________________|

About this LoRA:

1) This LoRA has been trained on images from the Anime Series >Violet Evergarden<.

2) Works well with characters and landscapes.

Checkpoints where this LoRA can really shine:

powercolorV1 + pastel-waifu-diffusion VAE

counterfeitV3.0

vrwaifumix_v20 (for landscapes)

>Trained with >CouterfeitV3.0<

>Recommendations:

-->LoRA strength: 0.8

-->Highres fix: Latent

-->Sampler: DPM++ 2M Karras

-->CFG scale: 7

__________________________________________________________________________________

Prompt example:

Prompt: 1girl, (masterpiece,best quality:1.6), scenery,night sky, open sky, stars, star light, milky way, starry sky, black_skirt, black shoes, full_body, green_eyes,necktie, pleated_skirt, dark blue hair, school_uniform, short_hair, short_sleeves, sweater_vest, white_shirt, short red hair, full body, standing,<lora:VioletEvergarden1.0:0.8>

Negative: EasyNegative, bad anatomy, bad hands, text, error, extra leg, extra finger, deformed fingers,extra person, extra character,forest, trees, objects, covered sky,

__________________________________________________________________________________

このLoRAについて

1) このLoRAは、アニメシリーズ >Violet Evergarden<の画像に学習させたものです。

2)キャラクターや風景に適しています。

このLoRAが活躍するチェックポイント

powercolorV1＋パステル和風拡散VAE

counterfeitV3.0

vrwaifumix_v20(風景用)

>CouterfeitV3.0<でトレーニング。

>おすすめです：

-->LoRA強度：0.8

-->Highres fix： Latent

-->サンプラー DPM++ 2M Karras

-->CFGスケール：7

__________________________________________________________________________________

关于这个LoRA：

1) 这个LoRA是在动漫系列>紫罗兰花园<的图像上训练的。

2) 对人物和风景的效果很好。

检查点，这个LoRA可以真正发挥其作用：

powercolorV1 + pastel-waifu-diffusion VAE

counterfeitV3.0

vrwaifumix_v20 (用于风景画)

>用>CouterfeitV3.0训练<

>建议：

-->LoRA强度: 0.8

-->Highres fix： Latent

-->采样器： DPM++ 2M Karras

-->CFG规模：7

modelVersions.description:
A merge of two of my LoRAs.

Changes:

-->More versatile in landscape generation.

-->Slightly more detailed.

-->Performs better with characters.

-->Works better with more checkpoints

------->Recommended: powercolor, anylora, cetusMix coda, daintyMixHentaiModel
